public class ProxoolDataSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.sql.DataSource, javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory

The Proxool DataSource implementation. Supports three modes of configuration:

  • pre-configured
  • bean-configured
  • factory-configured
